Welcome to this Lab

Here some link to deploy K8s and Matastor

** Install K8s master & workers **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/ubuntu-22.04.1/install-k8s.sh | sh -


** Mayastor prerequisite **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/mayastor/prerequisites.sh | sh -


** Deploy Mayastor **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/mayastor/deploy-mayastor.sh | sh -



** Create Mayastor pools **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/mayastor/create-pool-mayastor.sh | sh -

